        "uid": "7113"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t古粵語底層是藏緬語（源頭是西南，西南藏緬語），借詞層粵客贛層是華北中古漢語層（源頭是華北）\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-03-11",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "733633",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "raydalio",
        "uid": "26580"
